OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright end
OL,6,Fto the afternoon with a few isolated
OL,7,Fshowers lingering into the evening,
OL,8,Fhowever most places becoming dry
OL,9,Fovernight with cloudier skies
OL,10,Fdeveloping after midnight. Turning
OL,11,Fchilly with a touch of rural frost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA largely cloudy morning on
OL,14,FFriday with outbreaks of rain pushing
OL,15,Facross the region during the day.
OL,16,FStrengthening winds, these becoming
OL,17,Fgusty overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
